entry.title: Triplebyte Hiring Head of Engineering
entry.summary: Hello! We're hiring a Head of Engineering to join our core leadership team. We're building a job search platform that puts engineers in control, solves the problem of recruiter ghosting, and helps engineers without credentials break into the industry. This approach is growing quickly. The number of engineer joining Triplebtye grew 400% over the last quarter. We're looking for someone with startup engineering experience to help us scale our team.
